longBusinessSummary: Fastighets AB Trianon (publ), a real estate company, owns, builds, develops, and manages residential and commercial properties in Sweden. The company operates through Residential and Community/Commercial segments. It offers housing, retail, office, and public sector/community properties, as well as garage and parking spaces. The company was incorporated in 1973 and is based in Malmö, Sweden.
